/F1 9 Tf
10.3499999999999996 TL
0.278 0.333 0.412 rg
52. 500. Td
(Doctors do not need a dramatic monologue. They need a pattern they can trust. Bring at least a week of dated entries so the visit) Tj
T* (starts with evidence instead of reconstruction.) Tj
ET
BT
/F2 11 Tf
12.6499999999999986 TL
0.059 0.09 0.165 rg
44. 462. Td
(2. Sharp Description Beats Big Description) Tj
ET
BT
/F1 9 Tf
10.3499999999999996 TL
0.278 0.333 0.412 rg
52. 446. Td
(Where exactly? What kind of pain? When did it start, stop, move, or spike? Sharper routing through the facts is better than trying) Tj
T* (to make the pain sound impressive.) Tj
ET
BT
/F2 11 Tf
12.6499999999999986 TL
0.059 0.09 0.165 rg
44. 408. Td
(3. Function Is the Lever) Tj
ET
BT
/F1 9 Tf
10.3499999999999996 TL
0.278 0.333 0.412 rg
52. 392. Td
("Could not finish groceries" or "needed help showering" carries more weight than a floating number. Pain becomes clinically useful) Tj
T* (when it is tied to what the body could not do.) Tj
ET
